OL,3,CItchen Bridge charges increase for
OL,4,Cvisitors to Southampton
OL,6,FCharges to cross the Itchen Bridge
OL,7,Fhave increased for visitors to
OL,8,FSouthampton, as the city council try
OL,9,Fto raise money for repairs.
OL,11,FIt will see a 20p rise in tariffs for
OL,12,Fany road user who doesn't use a
OL,13,FSmartCities card, which can only be
OL,14,Fapplied for if you live in the city.
OL,16,FThis could see cars and light vans
OL,17,Fcharged up to #1.20, and large
OL,18,Fvehicles like HGVs, buses and coaches
OL,19,Fcharged up to #40 to cross.
