OL,3,CItchen Bridge charges increase for
OL,4,Cvisitors to Southampton
OL,6,FSouthampton City Council say the aim
OL,7,Fof the new tariffs is to ease
OL,8,Fcongestion in the city by encouraging
OL,9,Fvehicles to take other routes and to
OL,10,Fhelp fund maintenance on the bridge.
OL,12,FThe bridge, which links Woolston to
OL,13,FSouthampton City Centre, does not
OL,14,Freceive money from central government
OL,15,Fas it "does not serve a key strategic
OL,16,Ftransport route".
OL,18,FThe council says it's unusual for
OL,19,Flocal authorities to have sole
OL,20,Ffinancial responsibility for bridges
OL,21,Fof its size and structure.
