OL,3,CItchen Bridge charges increase for
OL,4,Cvisitors to Southampton
OL,6,FThe toll last went up in January 2024.
OL,8,FCouncillor Eammon Keogh, Cabinet
OL,9,FMember for Environment and Transport
OL,10,Fsaid: "I would encourage local people
OL,11,Fto sign up to the SmartCities scheme
OL,12,Fbecause Southampton residents with a
OL,13,FSmartCities card are unaffected by the
OL,14,Fnew toll.
OL,16,F"Residents can sign up to SmartCities
OL,17,For can collect an application form at
OL,18,FGateway or a Southampton City Council
OL,19,Flibrary."
